JAPANESE CITIZEN PRIVACY NOTICE
For consumers resident in Japan, notwithstanding any other provisions contained in this Global Privacy Statement, we will treat your Japanese Personal Identification Number (“My Number”) and its supporting documents in compliance with any applicable laws and regulations as described in this section.
We collect your My Number and supporting documents designated by us solely for the purpose of confirming your My Number as required by and in compliance with the Act on Submission of Statement of Overseas Wire Transfers for Purpose of Securing Proper Domestic Taxation of Japan (Act No. 110 of 1997, as amended).
